{"tid":745980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被問民族黨是否比三合會更危險    李家超：....","createTime":"2018-07-17T08:07:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T08:21:32.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dfdeb822c1833df3c09c90fde57252dfb481c64c","tid":745980,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:07:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1407404_1_L_20180717133558.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1407404_1_L_20180717133558.jpg&h=9aa220bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n保安局局長李家超表示，正考慮警方助理社團事務主任建議，決定是否行使《社團條例》並作出命令，禁止香港民族黨繼續運作。他說，今次是回歸以來，首次引用到有關條例。<br />\n<br />\n被問到是否意味民族黨比回歸以來成立的任何社團、包括三合會或犯罪組織更加危險。李家超重申，就有關個案，現階段不能亦不適宜談及太多細節，不想影響民族黨申述。<br />\n<br />\n被問到是否受到政治壓力，李家超說，今次是由助理社團事務主任按條例作決定，他會按條例考慮，按香港法例處理，強調是特區事務。他又被追問是否默認有政治壓力，李家超指，沒有這樣說，強調公平公正處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1407404-20180717.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1407404-20180717.htm&d=YXRUfOKYuqTA9jvC%2Bdoc5dtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=b91b73f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1407404-20180717.htm&h=cbd84162\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1407404-20180717.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d4c917f7aee75856af6023099a6ee74a92a7eefe","tid":745980,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:21:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/17/161807_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F17%2F161807_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=03429925&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}